{"id":451,"date":"2024-08-02T18:06:39","date_gmt":"2024-08-02T18:06:39","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/?post_type=wiki&#038;p=451"},"modified":"2024-08-02T18:06:39","modified_gmt":"2024-08-02T18:06:39","slug":"tm013-ice-beam","status":"publish","type":"wiki","link":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/tms-hms\/tm013-ice-beam\/","title":{"rendered":"TM013 Ice Beam"},"content":{"rendered":"<table class=\"table left grey\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\" class=\"text-large center\">TM013 Ice Beam<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Location<\/th>\n<td>Found in Icicle Cave 4F, in a small area that requires you to Surf to a hidden ladder on the third floor.<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Description<\/th>\n<td>The foe is struck with an icy beam. It may leave the foe with frostbite.<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>PP<\/th>\n<td>10<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Type<\/th>\n<td>Ice<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<h2>Prerequisites<\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Have access to Bellin Town<\/li>\n<li>Have <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/tms-hms\/hm03-surf\/\">Surf<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2>Location<\/h2>\n<p>Fly to the Bellin Town Pok\u00e9mon Center and take the North exit out of the town.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/01-pokemon-unbound-leaving-bellin-town.jpg\" alt=\"Leaving Bellin Town. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Leaving Bellin Town.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Continue heading North until you see the entrance to Icicle Cave, then head inside.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/02-pokemon-unbound-entering-icicle-cave.jpg\" alt=\"Entering Icicle Cave. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Entering Icicle Cave.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Inside, follow the path West.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/03-pokemon-unbound-following-the-path-west-in-icicle-cave.jpg\" alt=\"Following the path West in Icicle Cave. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Following the path West in Icicle Cave.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Go down the stairs to your South and take that ladder deeper into the cave.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/04-pokemon-unbound-taking-the-ladder-to-go-deeper-into-the-cave.jpg\" alt=\"Taking the ladder to go deeper into the cave. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Taking the ladder to go deeper into the cave.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Start going South after taking the ladder.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/05-pokemon-unbound-going-south-after-taking-the-ladder.jpg\" alt=\"Going South after taking the ladder. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Going South after taking the ladder.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You\u2019ll see some water you want to use Surf on to continue South.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/06-pokemon-unbound-using-surf-to-continue-going-south.jpg\" alt=\"Using Surf to continue going South. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Using Surf to continue going South.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Turn East to see a small frozen piece of land with a ladder you want to take up.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/07-pokemon-unbound-taking-the-ladder-to-the-secret-room.jpg\" alt=\"Taking the ladder to the secret room. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Taking the ladder to the secret room.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>The TM for Ice Beam is guarded by two trainers in this room.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/08\/08-pokemon-unbound-finding-the-tm-for-ice-beam.jpg\" alt=\"Finding the TM for Ice Beam. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Finding the TM for Ice Beam.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/tms-hms\/\" class=\"parent-page-card\">\n            <picture class=\"card-img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/tmloc.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/tmloc.png 200w, https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/tmloc-150x150.png 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" \/>\t\t\t\t            <\/picture>\n            <span class=\"card-info\">\n                <span class=\"card-info__caption\">Back to:<\/span>\n                <strong class=\"wiki-title\">TMs &#038; HMs<\/strong>\n            <\/span>\n        <\/a>\n\n\t\t\n","protected":false},"featured_media":452,"parent":139,"menu_order":0,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"categories":[8],"class_list":["post-451","wiki","type-wiki","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-tms-hms"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/451","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/wiki"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/139"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/452"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=451"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=451"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templa